"在首页「记录」模块点击「查看全部」或直接点击日历中的日期，可记录产蛋或洗澡情况。首页日历会用不同颜色标记不同事件。" = "Click \"View All\" in the \"Record\" module on the homepage or directly click on the date in the calendar to record egg laying or bathing. The home calendar will mark different events in different colors.";
"在首页点击「提醒」标签，点击「+」添加新提醒，设置提醒时间和重复周期即可。提醒会在设定时间推送通知。" = "Click the \"Reminder\" tab on the homepage, click \"+\" to add a new reminder, and set the reminder time and recurrence period. Reminders will send push notifications at the set time.";
"在首页点击「支出」标签，可以记录养鸟花费，支持多种类别（食物、玩具、医疗等）。关联多只鸟儿时，系统会自动平摊费用。" = "Click the \"Expenditure\" tab on the homepage to record bird raising expenses, supporting multiple categories (food, toys, medical care, etc.). When linking multiple birds, the system will automatically share the cost equally.";
"在首页点击鸟儿卡片进入详情页，点击「写日志」按钮，可以记录鸟儿的体重、饮食、心情、行为、健康状况等信息，还可以拍照记录。" = "Click the bird card on the homepage to enter the details page, and click the \"Write Log\" button to record the bird's weight, diet, mood, behavior, health status and other information, and you can also take photos for recording.";
"在鸟儿详情页点击「共享」按钮，输入家人的手机号，选择权限（主人/查看者）发送邀请。对方在「共享邀请」中接受后即可共同管理。" = "Click the \"Share\" button on the bird's details page, enter the family's mobile phone number, and select the permissions (owner/viewer) to send the invitation. After the other party accepts it in the \"Sharing Invitation\", they can manage it together.";
"在鸟儿详情页点击「编辑」按钮，可修改昵称、品种、性别、生日、羽色、来源、脚环编号、父母信息、病例记录等所有信息。清空某个字段后保存，该信息将被移除。" = "Click the \"Edit\" button on the bird details page to modify all information such as nickname, breed, gender, birthday, feather color, origin, anklet number, parent information, case records, etc. Clear a field and save, and the information will be removed.";
"在鸟儿详情页点击「编辑」，点击顶部的头像区域，选择「从相册选择」或「拍摄照片」，裁剪后头像将自动保存。离线时选择的头像会在联网后自动上传。" = "Click \"Edit\" on the bird details page, click the avatar area at the top, and select \"Select from Album\" or \"Take Photo\". The avatar will be automatically saved after cropping. The avatar selected while offline will be automatically uploaded when connected to the Internet.";
