"鸟儿张嘴呼吸、呼吸急促、尾巴随呼吸上下摆动，可能有喘息声或呼吸杂音。这是紧急情况，需立即处理。" = "The bird breathes with its mouth open, breathing rapidly, and its tail moves up and down with its breathing. There may be wheezing or breathing noises. This is an emergency situation and needs to be addressed immediately.";
"鸟儿打喷嚏，鼻孔周围可能有分泌物或结痂。偶尔打喷嚏可能是灰尘刺激，但频繁打喷嚏需要重视。" = "When a bird sneezes, there may be discharge or scabs around the nostrils. Occasional sneezing may be due to dust irritation, but frequent sneezing requires attention.";
"鸟儿档案" = "Bird Archives";
