"鸟鸟王国是一款专为爱鸟人士打造的宠物鸟管理应用。我们致力于帮助每一位鸟友更好地照顾自己的羽毛小伙伴，记录它们成长的每一个瞬间。" = "Bird Kingdom is a pet bird management application specially created for bird lovers. We are committed to helping every bird lover take better care of their feathered friends and record every moment of their growth.";
